           INITIALIZE                   TKJLR005-KEY

      *   그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-D-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  KJLR005-PK-GROUP-CO-CD
      *   기준년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-D-BASE-YMD
             TO  KJLR005-PK-BASE-YMD
      *   관리부점코드
           MOVE  WK-H-D-MGT-BRNCD
             TO  KJLR005-PK-MGT-BRNCD
      *   계좌번호
           MOVE  WK-H-D-ACNO
             TO  KJLR005-PK-ACNO

           #DYDBIO  SELECT-CMD-Y  TKJLR005-PK  TRJLR005-REC

      *@1 DBIO 처리결과확인 ERROR 처리
           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN COND-DBIO-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                MOVE 'KJLR005'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                MOVE 'SELECT'     TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                MOVE  SQLCODE     TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                MOVE 'SELECT시 오류가 발생했습니다'
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
      *@에러메시지:내부 본 처리
                #ERROR  CO-EBM05001 CO-UBM05001 CO-STAT-ERROR
                #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE

           #DYDBIO  DELETE-CMD-Y  TKJLR005-PK  TRJLR005-REC

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN COND-DBIO-OK
                ADD  CO-NUM-1           TO  WK-DELETE-CNT1

      *    DELETE 1000건 단위 COMMIT 처리
                INITIALIZE                      WK-AREA
                MOVE  'KJLR005'             TO  WK-TBL-ID
                MOVE  'NEXT'                TO  WK-FUNC-CD
                MOVE   WK-DELETE-CNT1       TO  WK-REC-CNT

                PERFORM  S8000-COMMIT-PROCESS-RTN
                   THRU  S8000-COMMIT-PROCESS-EXT
           WHEN COND-DBIO-MRNF
                #USRLOG '<< THKJLR005 DELETE OK >>'
           WHEN OTHER
                MOVE 'KJLR005'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                MOVE 'DELETE'     TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                MOVE  SQLCODE     TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                MOVE 'DELETE시 오류가 발생했습니다'
                                  TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
      *@에러메시지:내부 본 처리
                #ERROR  CO-EBM05001 CO-UBM05001 CO-STAT-ERROR
                #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE

